{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","symbolKind":"case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"placement would be laid out vertically.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out vertically."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","kind":"symbol"}}}